title: Kung Fu Panda's Jack Black Aligns His Famous Characters

media:group.media:title: Kung Fu Panda's Jack Black Aligns His Famous Characters
media:group.media:description:
"This is just the way the cookie crumbled." Jack Black joins us to breakdown his characters and rank them on the classic D&D (Dungeons & Dragons) Character Alignment Chart. From School of Rock's Dewey Finn to Kung Fu Panda's Po, Jack will decide once and for all just how chaotic they really are...
